---
Language: Cpp
BasedOnStyle: LLVM
IndentWidth: 4
DerivePointerAlignment: false
PointerAlignment: Left

# 配置代码格式化规则，用于实现连续参数和连续声明的对齐功能
# AlignAfterOpenBracket: Align - 设置在开括号后的参数对齐方式为对齐模式
# AlignConsecutiveAssignments: true - 启用连续赋值语句的对齐功能
# AlignConsecutiveDeclarations: true - 启用连续声明语句的对齐功能
# AllowAllArgumentsOnNextLine: false - 禁止将所有参数放在下一行
# BinPackParameters: false - 禁用参数的紧密排列，保持参数间适当的间距
# PenaltyBreakBeforeFirstCallParameter: 100 - 设置在第一个调用参数前换行的惩罚值为100

# 添加以下配置以实现连续参数、连续声明对齐
AlignAfterOpenBracket: Align
AlignConsecutiveAssignments: true
AlignConsecutiveDeclarations: true
AllowAllArgumentsOnNextLine: false
BinPackParameters: false
PenaltyBreakBeforeFirstCallParameter: 100
---

